{"tid":1511824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有人話唔好搞狗仔女，我真係得啖笑","createTime":"2019-08-27T15:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T19:43:05.000Z","uid":149250,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"66b7df0965b38d8d42bb62b118694c95eb03febc","tid":1511824,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"如果你真係選擇欺凌班警嘅細路 得罪講句你冇良知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511676</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓豬冇回應過任何野，你係咪帶風向自己諗啦。<br />\n屌你老母咁多人受左私刑你同我講唔好搞？禍必及妻兒呀大佬，仇恨黎架，你大愛唔代表人人都咁易放得低，啲學生係好無辜架，唔應該報係佢地身上架，咁多個手足呢屌你老母，咁我呢，有幾多個狗仔女係以為老豆係到警惡懲奸緊都未知，校院欺凌之前唔出黎講？發生左幾多呀，而家叫人唔好，屌你啦偽善撚"},{"pid":"da7266dda21a0bf775f23beab82ebfa42958ade8","tid":1511824,"uid":761,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"一定要搞！<br />\n打人地仔女唔洗付出代價？<br />\n學校戰線 正式啟動！"},{"pid":"0b7ed7106ddd96bfc7670e98f5ab579245ff024e","tid":1511824,"uid":122083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydPuQc-lij0&amp;has_verified=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DydPuQc-lij0%26has_verified%3D1&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=1339fa17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydPuQc-lij0&amp;has_verified=1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0039e273272647573b7fe7d589adbcb5e26d43a1","tid":1511824,"uid":8086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"偽善撚真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dd68a946c464adbd1eabfea03e65b1daaa6829","tid":1511824,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":